51
00:03:40,320 --> 00:03:41,720
Why were you so good to me?

52
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:44,360
Why did you make me fall in love with you?

53
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:47,920
Why?

54
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,240
Say something.

55
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,400
Say something.

56
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,040
Why?

57
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:51,720
I'm sorry.

58
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,000
I'm sorry.

59
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:10,580
I don't want to see you ever again.

60
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,120
Ziqing.

61
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,159
Ziqing.

62
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:41,850
My purpose for getting close to you

63
00:04:43,159 --> 00:04:44,400
